-- Lebanon’s Ex-Minister Charged With Terrorism, Al Jazeera Reports
-- B y   Z a i d   S a b a h   A b d   A l h a m i d
-- 2012-08-11T14:48:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-11/lebanon-s-ex-minister-charged-with-terrorism-al-jazeera-reports.html
A Lebanese court has charged former
Information Minister Michel Samaha with terrorism after he
admitted his role in a plot to carry out attacks in Lebanon with
the help of Syrian security agents,  Al Jazeera  reported, without
saying where it got the information.  Ali Mamlouk, head of Syria’s national security agency, was
also charged with terrorism, the broadcaster said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zaid Sabah Abd Alhamid in Washington at 
 zalhamid@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
